node.text: Bad first moto today but put together a pretty good ride in that second one. Happy with that and definitely something to build on👍🏼🤘🏼

node.text: Been struggling quite a bit with some things this season but appreciate the people that are still supporting me. The lows are part of life but just a reminder don’t ever judge someone based on what you “think” you know. Onto the next 🤘🏼🤘🏼

node.text: Not a great start to the season for me. Pala was ok some little mistakes and speed wasn’t quite there, I didn’t show up to Colorado I mean the 38 bike was out there but idk who was riding it cause that race was terrible, but at high point I finally found my speed as I turned some of the fastest laps both motos but a fall on lap one in the first moto and being in the first turn pile up in the second kept me out of the top battles. So way back to 7th in moto 1 and basically last to 6th in moto 2. Trying to improve every weekend, been struggling a little but we’ll be ight👍🏼
